        2 nori (seaweed) sheets
        1/2 lb sushi-grade tuna, thinly sliced
        1/2 cucumber, julienned
        1 avocado, sliced
        1 tbsp toasted sesame seeds
        Soy sauce, for dipping
        Pickled ginger (gari) and wasabi, for serving
        Instructions:
