        With wet hands, spread a thin layer of sushi rice evenly over the nori sheet, leaving about 1/2 inch of the nori uncovered at the top edge.
        Arrange slices of tuna, cucumber, and avocado horizontally across the center of the rice.
        Sprinkle toasted sesame seeds over the filling.
